<title>Credits</title>

<para>
Like other open source projects we want to thank some people for their help
and support. The following list is surely incomplete and we've forgoten
someone definitly, sorry for that! Just drop us a note, if you are not on
this list.
</para>

<para>
The following persons have especially pushed the project or are still
active supporters:
</para>

<para>
<itemizedlist>
  <listitem>
    <para>
    Robert Kehl, who has created the Win32-installer for the 1.x releases.
    Thanks a lot, Robert!
    </para>
